      <div class="card-teal-border"><p class="text-sm text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Industry directories</span> – Clutch, GoodFirms, G2, Capterra. AI platforms reference these for B2B recommendations.</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><p class="text-sm text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Case studies and research</span> – structured expertise that AI can extract and cite. Data beats opinion.</p></div>
    </div>
